data.description: Back on the market! This great home can still be yours.  Inspection & repairs done, plus roof certification. $5,000 offered towards buyer's closing costs. Nestled on 1.3 acres, this custom built move-in ready home is just under 2,300 SF and includes an additional 1,270 SF DETACHED 4 CAR GARAGE & WORKSHOP, COVERED DOUBLE RV PARKING PAD (w/ 30 AMP hookup), and a 2 Car attached Garage. Revel in the abundance of natural light that floods the split 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom open floorplan, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for entertaining or relaxation.  French doors open to the screened-in porch with a wood-burning fireplace and overlooks the large back yard and private preserve.  ***FEATURES & UPGRADES INCLUDE: Hardi plank exterior, Porcelain tile Floors, recessed lighting, tray ceilings, 12'+ high ceilings, NEW SS Appliances, granite counters, Ninja EPOXY floors in both garages, front and screened porches, sprinkler system with NEW dedicated well, NEW vinyl privacy FENCE, paid-in-full SOLAR PANELS (Avg $22/mo.), large walk -in closet with custom shelving and separate dedicated HVAC in owner's suite wing.  Add'l UPGRADES include Ultraviolet Halo installed in air handler that pulls the dust out of the air.  Cuts way down on dusting. Duct work was just cleaned.  Home SURGE protector and hurricane shutters.  ***LOCATION: Close to Benny Russell Park, Great schools, restaurants, shopping, Blackwater and Escambia rivers, Escambia Bay, Pensacola and Navarre Beaches. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home - schedule a tour today!
